$SIZES LIM1=503 $SIZES LIM2=503 $SIZES LIM6=503 $SIZES LTH=5 $SIZES PD=31
$PROBLEM NONCL
; PK model for simulation of drug concentration in central compartment ; with following characteristics: ; Compartments: 2 ; Elimination : linear ; Absorption : none (infusion/iv) ; Unit convention ; Dose: mg ; Concentration: ug/mL ; Time: hours ; The annotation of the parameter units is consistent with the given unit convention. ; Units of the inputs (dose) and outputs (concentration) in the dataset for parameter estimation need to match the unit convention.
$DATA ../../data/biExport.csv IGNORE=@
$INPUT SKIP SKIP SKIP ID TIME2 TIME TAD SKIP YTYPE SKIP SKIP DV SKIP SKIP CENS MDV EVID AMT CMT II ADDL SKIP TINF RATE SKIP SKIP
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN3 TRANS1
$PK ; Parameters
Tlag1 = 0
; MU Referencing MU_1 = THETA(1) ; CL MU_2 = THETA(2) ; Vc MU_3 = THETA(3) ; Q1 MU_4 = THETA(4) ; Vp1
; MU+ETA T_CL = MU_1 + ETA(1) T_Vc = MU_2 + ETA(2) T_Q1 = MU_3 + ETA(3) T_Vp1 = MU_4 + ETA(4)
; Parameter transformations CL = EXP(T_CL) Vc = EXP(T_Vc) Q1 = EXP(T_Q1) Vp1 = EXP(T_Vp1)
; Dosing compartments info F1 = 1; Ac
D1 = TINF ; TINF used if RATE=-2. If RATE=0 Bolus is made
; Define TIMEOFFSET TIMEOFFSET = TIME-TIME2
; ADVAN parameters K12 = Q1/Vc K21 = Q1/Vp1 K = -(-Q1/Vc - CL/Vc)-(Q1/Vc)
$ERROR ; States Ac = A(1) Ap1 = A(2)
; Variables Cc = Ac/Vc
; Just to avoid a NONMEM warning Y = 0 IPRED = 0 IRES = 0 W = 0 IWRES = 0
; Error model OUTPUT1 / Cc IF(YTYPE.EQ.1) THEN IPRED = Cc IRES = DV - IPRED W = SQRT(SIGMA(1))*IPRED IWRES = IRES/W Y = IPRED + EPS(1)*IPRED ENDIF
; Assign variables to report in tables ETA_CL = ETA(1) ETA_Vc = ETA(2) ETA_Q1 = ETA(3) ETA_Vp1 = ETA(4)
$THETA ; Model parameters -0.693147 ; 1 log(CL) (0.5) 2.30259 ; 2 log(Vc) (10) -2.99573 ; 3 log(Q1) (0.05) 2.30259 ; 4 log(Vp1) (10)
$OMEGA 0.5 STANDARD ; 1 CL 0.5 STANDARD ; 2 Vc 0.5 STANDARD ; 3 Q1 0.5 STANDARD ; 4 Vp1
$SIGMA ; Error model parameters in variances 0.09 ; (0.3)**2 Relative / Proportional error OUTPUT1
$ESTIMATION METHOD=ITS INTERACTION NOABORT NITER=10 SIGDIGITS=3 PRINT=1
$ESTIMATION METHOD=SAEM INTERACTION RANMETHOD=P NOABORT NBURN=50 NITER=20 ISAMPLE=1 CONSTRAIN=7 CTYPE=0 SEED=123456 POSTHOC SIGDIGITS=3 PRINT=1
$ESTIMATION METHOD=IMP INTERACTION RANMETHOD=P NOABORT EONLY=1 ISAMPLE=1000 NITER=10 MAPITER=0 SIGDIGITS=3 PRINT=1 SEED=123456
$COVARIANCE UNCONDITIONAL MATRIX=S PRINT=E
$TABLE ID TIME TIME2 TAD YTYPE MDV EVID CENS DV IPRED IRES IWRES NPDE EPRED=XPRED ERES=XRES EWRES=XWRES NOPRINT ONEHEADER NOAPPEND FILE=project.pred FORMAT=s1PG15.6 ESAMPLE=1000 SEED=123456
$TABLE ID ETA_CL ETA_Vc ETA_Q1 ETA_Vp1 NOPRINT ONEHEADER FIRSTONLY NOAPPEND FILE=project.eta FORMAT=s1PG15.6
$TABLE ID CL Vc Q1 Vp1 NOPRINT ONEHEADER FIRSTONLY NOAPPEND FILE=project.indiv FORMAT=s1PG15.6
